reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 21, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars High quality for great price!
reviews.reviewText: Color is nice and matches advertising, made sturdy- item has weight to it. True to size ordered 2X size, but was too big, however, good if you want to still layer and for bigger people. Will keep you super warm only issue is sleeves are longer due to larger sizing, so keep that in mind, if you are shorter in height. Also long in length so no worries about butt or legs getting frozen. Thank you!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 20, 2023
reviews.reviewText: I received the coat 4-5 days ago and I’m blown away by how it meets all my needs at such a low price. I shopped several websites, looking for just the right coat. I have a puffer jacket that is really warm, and I wanted the same in a full-length coat. I walk my dog every morning, and it can be very cold because we have windy weather that makes cold feel even colder. It takes a really good coat to stop the wind from penetrating the outer layer of protection.This coat is very well made and it fits perfectly. I love that it has a two-way zipper so that it can e zipped up from the bottom to allow you to sit more comfortably. It’s a good weight. Not too heavy, but definitely heavy enough to be warm. A plus is that it is a pretty colorand is a nice material. I love this coat!!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 4, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Nice, but big
reviews.reviewText: So glad I paid attention to the comments about the size. I originally wanted a 2X because I wanted a roomy coat that I could wear with sweaters, sweats, etc. But I ended up going smaller with an XL. Even with that it's a bit bigger than anticipated. But that's the only issue. It's warm, comfortable and attractive. I highly recommend it, just go with 2 sizes smaller than you normally would.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 5, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars You Need This Coat!
reviews.reviewText: I LOVE THIS COAT!!! I am a SM Girl. I have a coat from him and was looking for another. I selected brown. The Color is rich and the fabric strong and it is WARM. As the other reviews stated, it runs large so I bought 1 size down. The best part was a surprise, The Length! It is perfect in cold wind and rain! Deep pockets and a bottom up zipper for movement. The quality for the price? Amazing! It was perfect out of the packaging!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 6, 2024
reviews.reviewText: I love everything about this coat. I ordered a size large and it fits nicely giving me enough room to layer or wear thick sweatshirts and sweaters. I love the detailed stiching at the wrists, the elastic synching on the back, the snaps on the bottom of the back, the zipper that zips from the top and from the bottom, the deep pockets with zippers, and the length of the coat. The size of the hood is perfect and doesn't fall in my face. It's a warm coat, but not too heavy or bulky. It's a great, stylish winter coat. Just what I was looking for.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 16, 2024
reviews.reviewText: I live in MN and needed a long coat to keep me warm in the long and cold winters. I personally think this coat runs a little large. I originally ordered a large, knowing I wanted to be able to wear bulky sweaters and sweatshirts underneath. The large was quite large and allowed too much air to flow up and into the coat. I returned the large and ordered a MEDIUM and it fits perfectly. Fitted in the chest, but not too tight, and the cinching on the back of the coat provides a nice fitted look. With the coat being really long, just about at my ankles, I like that the zipper unzips from the bottom to make it easier getting in and out of vehicles.My measurements are: 38DD and typically a size large in clothing

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 26, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 3.0 out of 5 stars Nice Coat for the Price....
reviews.reviewText: I ordered this to wear for car duty at my school. We had a cold snap in Texas (27 degrees) and my legs were freezing while wearing this! I may not know how a coat should protect you from the cold because I have always lived in Texas, but I was disappointed. Also runs a little big.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 7, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Great buy for the price. Cozy, light weight. Perfect in these winter storms.
reviews.reviewText: Love the flattering fit. I did have to size down. Big! The zipper is sticking or difficult to start at bottom. So, old time remedy, I waxed the zipper teeth and bottom zipper start. That helped. But now I don't completely unzip it and just leave the bottom 10 inches zipped and step out of the coat.I got it on sale in Dusty Rose, Champagne,Black and White for less than $225. I work outside alot and I can be rough on coats,so perfect deal !

reviews.reviewTitle: Lovely coat but way too big!
reviews.reviewText: Beautiful coat. Exactly what I was after, including colour and style. After reading the reviews, I decided to order one size down (Small). Unfortunately, the fit was still too big and there was no XS available. I loved the coat so much that I even took it to a tailor to see if they could take alter it for me, but the work would have been just too extensive. Had to pay shipping to return, but vendor communication was excellent and the refund was prompt.
Ya había comprado otros colores XL,pero ya me quedan grandes y compré este color en talla G me encantó y como queda el talle y como ajusta a la cintura,muy calientito.

Me quedó muy grande. Pero no de mangas porque tengo brazos largos. No lo voy a cambiar porque así puedo usarlo con un suéter grueso abajo y no se va a ver apretado.Es Madden Girl y está acabado muy fino y perfecto además de que es súper calientito!

On the positive side, it arrived within 1 week, well packaged and without flaws. The price was right. The titanium colour is a lovely taupe and the fabric has a nice sheen. It was the right length for me. Unfortunately, the Medium size was too big in the sleeves, around the waist and hips and the pockets were too deep. I returned it the next day.
True to size. Don't use the size chart
